examples.en: She repaired to him for help.
Where can I get my shoes repaired?
They repaired daily to the park.
They repaired to the judge's chambers.
We repaired the hull below the waterline.
We'll leave on Tuesday  always assuming the car's repaired by then.
They sportingly agreed to postpone the race until our boat was repaired.
The equipment is complex and requires specialist knowledge to be repaired.
A whole house was placed in their hands, to be thoroughly cleansed and repaired.
The painting was successfully repaired in time for the opening of the exhibition.
I think we paid too much for the house, considering that we needed to get the roof repaired.
